<I>Sat, 7 Jan 1995 18:35:06 -0500 (EST)</I>
<P>
I believe Tim Oren of <A HREF="http://www.compuserve.com">Compuserve</A>
has made an error in chronology.
<P>
When the GIF standard was initially developed in 1987, Unisys was not
"pursuing" a patent for the
<A HREF="gopher://wiretap.spies.com:70/00/Library/Techdoc/Misc/lzwexp.txt">LZW</A>
algorithm; the patent had already been
awarded, in 1985.
