I was surprised to receive the following bounce:
<P>
&gt;Subject: Error Condition Re: Re: Female blues guitarists summary<BR>
&gt;X-Listprocessor-Version: 6.0c -- ListProcessor by Anastasios Kotsikonas<BR>
&gt;X-Comment: Folk Music Mailing List
<P>
