&gt;If your posting was intentional, please accept our apologies and resend your<BR>
&gt;mail message, making sure you do not include anything that may look like a<BR>
&gt;request in the first line of the body of the actual message. If this was <BR>
&gt;indeed a request please resend it to <A HREF="mailto:listserver@nysernet.org">listserver@nysernet.org</A>
