<DD><A HREF="#subj6.1">Rich Lethin</A><BR>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT="o" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14">
<A HREF="#subj7">MS-Word "Find File" feature scales poorly with MAE/NFS</A>
<DD><A HREF="#subj7.1">Jeff Anderson-Lee</A><BR>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT="o" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14">
